    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Well-kept classic in good overall condition with a clean, honest presentation and the kind of cared-for feel that makes it easy to enjoy right away. It shows nicely throughout, with solid paint, a tidy interior, and good trim and brightwork for a driver-quality example. A very appealing car for someone looking for a good classic that presents well and can be driven, shown, and enjoyed with confidence.",
