    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "$46,500 - Mint-condition car that presents exceptionally well inside and out. The body and paint look very clean, the interior is tidy and well-kept, and it shows none of the noticeable wear you\u2019d expect from an average used vehicle. This is the kind of car a buyer can feel good about driving home right away, with strong cosmetic appeal and no obvious condition-related compromises.",
